OL,3,CPoor maternity care 'tolerated as
OL,4,Cnormal', report finds
OL,6,FITV News Reporter Charlie Frost
OL,7,Fanalyses the key findings from the
OL,8,Finquiry
OL,10,FA parliamentary inquiry into birth
OL,11,Ftrauma is calling for a national plan
OL,12,Fto improve care after it heard
OL,13,F"harrowing" evidence from thousands of
OL,14,Fwomen.
OL,16,FThe all-party inquiry, led by
OL,17,FConservative MP Theo Clarke and Labour
OL,18,FMP Rosie Duffield, is due to publish
OL,19,Fits findings on Monday.
