OL,3,CPoor maternity care 'tolerated as
OL,4,Cnormal', report finds
OL,6,FITV's Good Morning Britain heard from
OL,7,Fone woman who described the first of
OL,8,Fher three births as the "most
OL,9,Fterrifying experience" of her life,
OL,10,Fafter a nurse wrongly administered an
OL,11,Fepidural.
OL,13,FMore than 1,300 women gave testimony
OL,14,Fto the inquiry, which, according to
OL,15,FThe Times, found "poor care is all
OL,16,Ffrequently tolerated as normal, and
OL,17,Fwomen are treated as an inconvenience".
