OL,3,CPoor maternity care 'tolerated as
OL,4,Cnormal', report finds
OL,6,FA third of those who took part said
OL,7,Fthat they experienced traumatic
OL,8,Fbirths, while one out of 25 were left
OL,9,Fwith post traumatic stress disorder
OL,10,F(PTSD).
OL,12,FDivina Johnson, who had three
OL,13,Ftraumatic births, said she felt
OL,14,Freduced to a "vessel that had a baby"
OL,15,Fwhile receiving childbirth care.
OL,17,FShe said: "I felt like a problem that
OL,18,Fjust needed to be sorted, like get
OL,19,Fthis woman to have her baby so that we
OL,20,Fcan move onto the next."
