OL,6,FMs Johnson added that she faced racist
OL,7,Ftreatment from one consultant who
OL,8,Fallegedly told her "I expect your kind
OL,9,Fto be stronger than this".
OL,11,FAmong the recommendations included in
OL,12,Fthe report is the creation of a
OL,13,Fmaternity commissioner reporting to
OL,14,Fthe prime minister.
