OL,3,CPoor maternity care 'tolerated as
OL,4,Cnormal', report finds
OL,6,FNHS England chief executive Amanda
OL,7,FPritchard said the experiences of the
OL,8,Fwomen who gave evidence to the inquiry
OL,9,Fwere "simply not good enough".
OL,11,FHealth Secretary Victoria Atkins said
OL,12,Fshe was "determined to improve the
OL,13,Fquality and consistency of care for
OL,14,Fwomen throughout pregnancy, birth and
OL,15,Fthe critical months that follow".
OL,17,FIn January, she shared her personal
OL,18,Fexperience of the "darker corners" of
OL,19,Fthe NHS, after giving birth as a
OL,20,Fpatient with type one diabetes.
